{"tid":1405349,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"消閒資訊類傳媒工作者給香港人的信 8 月 5 日齊罷工","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T22:23:33.000Z","uid":111235,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6d89a92e80a1d9c5f7fd711e6a0b0fc7f528cc","tid":1405349,"uid":111235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"致香港人<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群熱愛香港的「消閒資訊類」傳媒工作者。在反修訂逃犯條例風波中，我們感謝前線港聞記者及攝影記者一直謹守崗位，為報道事實真相而奔波。<br />\n<br />\n8 月 5 日，我們會罷工。<br />\n<br />\n有人或會質疑傳媒工作者罷工有違新聞專業操守，但我們這群主要報道生活及消費資訊的記者，在大是大非之下，認為應該放下「食買玩」鋼筆，站出來響應罷工，以和平理性的方式，撐前線採訪記者，並一同捍衛新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n我們懇請政府，立即回應民間提出的五大訴求。而站於傳媒工作者角度，我們同時希望新聞自由能獲得保障，並譴責警方多次阻礙記者的採訪工作，甚至暴力對待記者。<br />\n<br />\n8 月 5 日，全民罷工。香港人加油，一同為香港的未來努力！<br />\n<br />\n一群來自不同傳媒機構的傳媒工作者敬上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171357_7fb77c07f36526382309f7c2504a2ee3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171357_7fb77c07f36526382309f7c2504a2ee3.jpg&h=62c52be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171359_a96e74394cca3082349ad130038d44e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171359_a96e74394cca3082349ad130038d44e5.jpg&h=50d9e12f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171401_73fff76d2bca0ce093a08963a3774fb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171401_73fff76d2bca0ce093a08963a3774fb4.jpg&h=92dd30db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171403_68f29599e85562c67ac24e15c171ded3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171403_68f29599e85562c67ac24e15c171ded3.jpg&h=ccdf5c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171405_bdb4655f8b07cb3030655aaebca92c6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171405_bdb4655f8b07cb3030655aaebca92c6a.jpg&h=48fa29e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171407_b9f36368a5624b882db811ea76892ad2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171407_b9f36368a5624b882db811ea76892ad2.jpg&h=1c3a62b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171410_5d515adff8b65cef70175c293e5b6799.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171410_5d515adff8b65cef70175c293e5b6799.jpg&h=4ffebdac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171412_6a4a2d2d08dcb1d6f1b2650d7a680b35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171412_6a4a2d2d08dcb1d6f1b2650d7a680b35.jpg&h=6897f09c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171420_230425bbb0ae5c4323c6b0b64295c925.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171420_230425bbb0ae5c4323c6b0b64295c925.jpg&h=251f2677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/171437_9f1b3c3e6b37ed3a4d0b8c5abdd76741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F171437_9f1b3c3e6b37ed3a4d0b8c5abdd76741.jpg&h=bd5f4da3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d73edb8b8e66b50d0aa93b375cc3f59875e9c745","tid":1405349,"uid":238275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XiiNef8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiiNef8.png&h=ca4da279&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1e8a89f576d63a7beab861203f3d05f5b32751b","tid":1405349,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:24:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"72919e37379ae79803b5806c2d6994295a68c2e9","tid":1405349,"uid":69876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148b6037023f0e35d7559459d3dd8f0a1740e788","tid":1405349,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e69c1a5ff62fcd3c3a94d0aeb46231651219f65e","tid":1405349,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1a578ccc302e481c58b68439e90eece4d0864b","tid":1405349,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:52:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">好多人都因為各種原因<br />\n唔能夠85罷工<br />\n佢地絕對需要<span style=\"color: red;\">被罷工</span><br />\n佢地都好為香港出一分力<br />\n各位連登仔/港鐵站車長站長<br />\n請幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n致各司機<br />\n堵塞各個主要交通幹道<br />\n屯門公路/大欖隧道/青馬大橋/獅子山隧道/大老山隧道/觀塘迴旋處/紅隧等等<br />\n各式各樣<span style=\"color: red;\">交通意外</span><br />\n請各位司機配合<br />\n真正全民大罷工！<br />\n8月5日香港需要你<br />\n<br />\n致港鐵車長站長<br />\n大圍/九龍塘/紅磡/調景嶺/金鐘/旺角/西鐵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5:00</span>開始全民不合作運動<br />\n各連登仔幫忙<span style=\"color: red;\">接力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用最少資源做到最大效益<br />\n港鐵快跑運動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">急停制/路軌/車長室/火警鐘撳手</span>等等<br />\n分3/4 team人可癱瘓一個上午</span><br />\n港鐵車長/站長可<span style=\"color: red;\">按章工作</span><br />\n幫幫忙盡量拖延時間<br />\n香港人需要你</span></span>"},{"pid":"c056900e88d02191538b14350336c5aec9a8fafe","tid":1405349,"uid":90560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:28:00.000Z","msg":"we connect"},{"pid":"e223698301fef046451f74305d31b92050bace9d","tid":1405349,"uid":74764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"01咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ad24046b0d42da479670e549423db10a4a4bd4","tid":1405349,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"9f1c54aa247255c3bc2dd13800de9eea8de61451","tid":1405349,"uid":114701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"行家加油!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ab0a7fb02079e97b6f8f4731c29b86e79ac191","tid":1405349,"uid":69876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:09:12.000Z","msg":"罷工罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59907a0d72d1ddc16f3901bac2adc4e1773c3b42","tid":1405349,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:16:51.000Z","msg":"01 都有咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace22f2b1e429da1bc5024a1304c67fcc4d511e0","tid":1405349,"uid":15930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:34:16.000Z","msg":"行家加油！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6210713fd7421de932fd0726c51f86d71c3eddec","tid":1405349,"uid":69876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲做記者，好多人都係有團火，前線行家加油"},{"pid":"9ada539687ec964cc76eb95776088f2a72e33588","tid